title: D2 Bot lane LFT based in Melbourne to compete in lans
body: Hey, if you're reading this me and my friend are looking for a team I'm currently diamond 2 and my support is silver 3 that peaked diamond two seasons ago. We are looking to compete in lans and maybe the OOL we have a lot of experience and are able to team fight extremely well I'm available every day apart from friday 5-10 as is my supports. Both of our champion pools include 4+ champs in that specific lane.
